physiotherapist or a Yorisoi (snuggling nursing robot) robot applies a light 
force in the direction of the positive axis, it is possible to prevent a 
fall.Assertive technology, such as the Yorisoi robot, may be used to improve the 
safety TUG test in patients with PD.

