Published by Elsevier Masson SAS. All rights reserved.

DOI: 10.1016/j.canrad.2021.05.007
PMID: 34175226 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


820. J Vasc Surg. 2021 Dec;74(6):2030-2039.e2. doi: 10.1016/j.jvs.2021.05.049.
